    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Dorcroast, the invigorating cold brew coffee inspired by the triumph over darkness in Ustalav, awakens your senses with a bittersweet symphony. With a delightful spritz of energy, Dorcroast revitalizes your day, infusing it with the indomitable spirit that arises from the genocide of one's enemies. This remarkable brew serves as a tribute to the resilience of those who stood against evil, reminding you that even in the face of adversity, there is always room for celebration and the promise of a brighter tomorrow.</p><p><em>Brewed and Bottled in Caliphas.</em></p><img src=\"Art%20-%20Items/potions/coffee_in_a_bottle_dd_magic_item_arcanograph.webp\" />",
